{"word":"γαίω","slug":"γαίω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>γαίω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>The Root was <el>ΓΑΥ</el>, or <el>ΓΑϜ</el>, <a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <a href='S:γαῦρος'><el>γαῦρος</el></a>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>gaudium</el>.\n<p/><i>to exult</i>, only in <a href='S:participle'>part.</a> <el>κύδεϊ γαίων</el> <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/>"}]}